          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At some time or other the Lord will provide:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It may not be my time, it may not be thy time;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And yet in His own time, “the Lord will provide.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then we’ll trust in the Lord, and He will provide;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, we’ll trust in the Lord, and He will provide."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Despond then no longer; the Lord will provide:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And this be the token—no word He hath spoken"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Was ever yet broken: “The Lord will provide.”"
            }
          ]
